  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Land Surveyor",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Description</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Lead, manage and plan the site activities related to surveying</li>\n  <li>Setting up of Survey-Points and levels on site</li>\n  <li>Plan and coordinate daily survey activity</li>\n  <li>Maintenance of surveying instrumentation such as Total Station, levelling instrument etc.</li>\n  <li>Assist production team to produce shop drawings, as built survey drawings and actual works - setting out if required.</li>\n  <li>Ensure all readings are taken on a timely, efficient and accurate basis.</li>\n  <li>Attend site meeting and liaise closely with client on land surveying matters</li>\n  <li>To carry out site inspection from time to time as part of project quality control.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Job Requirements</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum 3 years of working experience as a land surveyor</li>\n  <li>Diploma or Bachelor's Degree in relevant field</li>\n  <li>Must have experience working in HDB projects</li>\n  <li>Must be a member of SISV</li>\n</ul>",
